  <body dur="03:40.660">
    <div begin="00:14.560" end="03:40.660">
      <p begin="00:14.560" end="00:16.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:14.560" end="00:14.950">The</span> <span begin="00:15.020" end="00:15.370">en</span><span begin="00:15.370" end="00:15.400">d</span> <span begin="00:15.400" end="00:15.540">i</span><span begin="00:15.540" end="00:15.680">s</span> <span begin="00:15.680" end="00:15.960">dis</span><span begin="00:15.960" end="00:16.390">tan</span><span begin="00:16.390" end="00:16.440">t</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">终点依然遥不可及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">終點依然遙不可及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">終わりはまだ遠い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝은 아득하게 멀어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La fin est lointaine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El final está distante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Ende ist fern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fim está distante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Конец еще далек</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La fine è distante</span></p>
      <p begin="00:16.870" end="00:21.620" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:16.870" end="00:17.030">Lo</span><span begin="00:17.030" end="00:17.190">st</span> <span begin="00:17.190" end="00:17.540">in</span> <span begin="00:17.540" end="00:17.690">de</span><span begin="00:17.740" end="00:18.030">ser</span><span begin="00:18.030" end="00:18.130">t</span> <span begin="00:18.180" end="00:18.510">sand</span><span begin="00:18.510" end="00:18.610">s,</span> <span begin="00:18.730" end="00:18.890">wi</span><span begin="00:18.890" end="00:18.970">th</span> <span begin="00:19.050" end="00:19.330">no</span> <span begin="00:19.380" end="00:19.650">gui</span><span begin="00:19.650" end="00:19.970">ding</span> <span begin="00:20.040" end="00:20.320">pa</span><span begin="00:20.320" end="00:20.360">th</span> <span begin="00:20.360" end="00:20.520">a</span><span begin="00:20.520" end="00:21.620">head</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">迷失在狂沙之中 前路毫无指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">迷失在狂沙之中 前路毫無指引</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">導く道もなく 砂漠の砂に迷い込む</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사막의 모래 속에 길을 잃고, 앞을 이끌어줄 길도 없이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Perdue dans les sables du désert sans aucun chemin pour me guider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Perdida en las arenas del desierto, sin un camino que me guíe por delante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verloren im Wüstensand ohne einen Wegweiser voraus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perdida nas areias do deserto, sem nenhum caminho a seguir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Потеряна в песках пустыни без путеводной нити впереди</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Persa nelle sabbie del deserto senza alcun sentiero a guidarmi</span></p>
      <p begin="00:22.370" end="00:26.000" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:22.370" end="00:22.720">In</span> <span begin="00:22.720" end="00:22.960">my</span> <span begin="00:23.010" end="00:23.210">heart,</span> <span begin="00:23.300" end="00:23.470">a</span> <span begin="00:23.470" end="00:23.580">s</span><span begin="00:23.630" end="00:23.910">torm</span> <span begin="00:24.020" end="00:24.090">o</span><span begin="00:24.090" end="00:24.180">f</span> <span begin="00:24.180" end="00:24.580">fee</span><span begin="00:24.580" end="00:24.740">ling</span><span begin="00:24.740" end="00:24.940">s</span> <span begin="00:24.940" end="00:25.130">a</span><span begin="00:25.200" end="00:25.610">ri</span><span begin="00:25.830" end="00:26.000">ses</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我的心中 掀起情感的风暴</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我的心中 掀起情感的風暴</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">胸の内に 感情の嵐が巻き起こる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 마음속엔, 감정의 폭풍이 일어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans mon cœur une tempête de sentiments s'élève</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En mi corazón, se levanta una tormenta de sentimientos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In meinem Herzen zieht ein Sturm der Gefühle auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em meu coração, surge uma tempestade de sentimentos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В моем сердце поднимается буря чувств</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Nel mio cuore si solleva una tempesta di sentimenti</span></p>
      <p begin="00:26.000" end="00:29.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:26.000" end="00:26.260">Yet</span> <span begin="00:26.540" end="00:26.760">one</span> <span begin="00:26.940" end="00:27.210">grain</span> <span begin="00:27.440" end="00:27.590">o</span><span begin="00:27.590" end="00:27.670">f</span> <span begin="00:27.710" end="00:28.050">hope</span> <span begin="00:28.100" end="00:28.250">re</span><span begin="00:28.370" end="00:28.650">main</span><span begin="00:28.650" end="00:28.790">s</span> <span begin="00:28.790" end="00:29.370">he</span><span begin="00:29.370" end="00:29.490">re</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">然而这里 仍残存着一缕希望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">然而這裡 仍殘存著一縷希望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">それでも一粒の希望がここに残る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 한 알의 희망이 이곳에 남아있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourtant un seul grain d'espoir subsiste ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sin embargo un grano de esperanza permanece aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Doch ein Körnchen Hoffnung bleibt hier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ainda assim um grão de esperança permanece aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Но здесь остается еще одна крупица надежды</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Eppure qui rimane un granello di speranza</span></p>
      <p begin="00:29.990" end="00:33.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:29.990" end="00:30.430">永</span><span begin="00:30.670" end="00:31.150">遠</span><span begin="00:31.360" end="00:31.500">と</span><span begin="00:31.600" end="00:32.020">見</span><span begin="00:32.080" end="00:32.620">紛</span><span begin="00:32.620" end="00:32.740">う</span><span begin="00:32.740" end="00:32.940">闇</span><span begin="00:32.990" end="00:33.380">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">与那仿佛化作永恒的黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">與那彷彿化作永恆的黑暗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With darkness mistaken for eternity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">영원이라 착각할 듯한 어둠과</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec des ténèbres qu'on prendrait pour l'éternité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con una oscuridad que se confunde con la eternidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Dunkelheit die man mit der Ewigkeit verwechselt und</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com a escuridão que se confunde com a eternidade e</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тьма которую можно принять за вечность и</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Con un'oscurità che si confonde con l'eternità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Eien to mimagau yami to</span></p>
      <p begin="00:33.680" end="00:37.110" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:33.680" end="00:33.850">孤</span><span begin="00:33.920" end="00:34.560">独</span><span begin="00:34.610" end="00:34.800">が</span><span begin="00:35.060" end="00:35.590">疼</span><span begin="00:35.680" end="00:35.800">く</span><span begin="00:35.800" end="00:36.010">伽</span><span begin="00:36.010" end="00:36.590">藍</span><span begin="00:36.660" end="00:37.110">堂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">以及孤独隐隐作痛的空洞躯壳</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">以及孤獨隱隱作痛的空洞軀殼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">An empty shell where loneliness aches</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">고독이 쑤셔오는 텅 빈 공간</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une salle vide où la solitude me fait souffrir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y un vacío donde duele la soledad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine leere Hülle in der die Einsamkeit schmerzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O vazio onde a solidão lateja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пустота ноющая от одиночества</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un tempio vuoto dove pulsa la solitudine</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kodoku ga uzuku garandou</span></p>
      <p begin="00:37.350" end="00:40.590" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:37.350" end="00:37.440">ゆ</span><span begin="00:37.470" end="00:37.570">ら</span><span begin="00:37.610" end="00:37.840">り</span><span begin="00:38.050" end="00:38.170">揺</span><span begin="00:38.170" end="00:38.270">れ</span><span begin="00:38.310" end="00:38.560">て</span><span begin="00:38.760" end="00:38.890">揺</span><span begin="00:38.890" end="00:39.020">れ</span><span begin="00:39.020" end="00:39.240">る</span><span begin="00:39.440" end="00:39.690">君</span><span begin="00:39.720" end="00:39.910">の</span><span begin="00:40.090" end="00:40.350">声</span><span begin="00:40.390" end="00:40.590">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是你那摇曳不定 飘忽的声音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是你那搖曳不定 飄忽的聲音</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">By your swaying swaying swaying voice</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아른아른 흔들리며 요동치는 너의 목소리에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Par ta voix qui vacille et tremble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por tu voz que oscila temblando temblando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Von deiner Stimme die sanft schwankt und bebt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Na sua voz que balança e balança suavemente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Твой голос что так мягко и плавно звучит</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dalla tua voce che tremola e oscilla dolcemente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yurari yurete yureru kimi no koe ni</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.820" end="00:44.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:40.820" end="00:41.060">生</span><span begin="00:41.280" end="00:41.490">か</span><span begin="00:41.710" end="00:41.990">さ</span><span begin="00:42.220" end="00:42.340">れ</span><span begin="00:42.420" end="00:42.660">て</span><span begin="00:42.660" end="00:42.800">い</span><span begin="00:42.860" end="00:43.100">た</span> <span begin="00:43.160" end="00:43.460">Mid</span><span begin="00:43.620" end="00:44.400">night</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我在那午夜 苟延残喘至今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我在那午夜 苟延殘喘至今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I was kept alive Midnight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">生かされていた 真夜中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">살아갈 수 있었어, 이 깊은 밤을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai été maintenue en vie à minuit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me mantenía con vida en la medianoche</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wurde ich am Leben gehalten um Mitternacht</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu fui mantida viva Midnight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сохранял мне жизнь в эту полночь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Venivo tenuta in vita a mezzanotte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ikasarete ita Midnight</span></p>
      <p begin="00:44.750" end="00:46.400" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:44.750" end="00:44.880">果</span><span begin="00:44.970" end="00:45.080">て</span><span begin="00:45.170" end="00:45.440">し</span><span begin="00:45.440" end="00:45.610">な</span><span begin="00:45.610" end="00:45.670">い</span><span begin="00:45.750" end="00:46.050">光</span><span begin="00:46.130" end="00:46.400">景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无边无际的光景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無邊無際的光景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Endless scene</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝없는 광경</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un paysage sans fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un paisaje interminable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein endloser Anblick</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cenário sem fim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бескрайние пейзажи</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Uno scenario sconfinato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hateshinai koukei</span></p>
      <p begin="00:46.620" end="00:48.180" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:46.620" end="00:46.920">懐</span><span begin="00:47.060" end="00:47.150">か</span><span begin="00:47.260" end="00:47.540">しい</span><span begin="00:47.610" end="00:47.930">情</span><span begin="00:47.970" end="00:48.180">景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">令人怀念的情景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">令人懷念的情景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Nostalgic sight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리운 정경</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une scène nostalgique</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una escena nostálgica</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine nostalgische Szene</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cena nostálgica</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Знакомые до боли сцены</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una scena nostalgica</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Natsukashii joukei</span></p>
      <p begin="00:48.420" end="00:50.050" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:48.420" end="00:48.570">た</span><span begin="00:48.660" end="00:48.780">だ</span><span begin="00:48.840" end="00:49.290">一</span><span begin="00:49.320" end="00:49.480">つ</span><span begin="00:49.480" end="00:49.730">だ</span><span begin="00:49.830" end="00:50.050">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唯有那唯一的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唯有那唯一的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Only one thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">오직 단 하나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Juste une seule chose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo hay una cosa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur eines allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas um único</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И лишь одна</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Soltanto uno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tada hitotsu dake</span></p>
      <p begin="00:50.290" end="00:51.920" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:50.290" end="00:50.430">待</span><span begin="00:50.480" end="00:50.700">ち</span><span begin="00:50.740" end="00:51.180">望</span><span begin="00:51.180" end="00:51.300">む</span><span begin="00:51.300" end="00:51.920">夢…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我所期盼的梦境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我所期盼的夢境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The dream I long for...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">고대하는 꿈…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le rêve que j'attendais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El sueño que tanto anhelo…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der lang ersehnte Traum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sonho que anseio...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Желанная мечта</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il sogno che attendo con ansia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Machinozomu yume…</span></p>
      <p begin="00:53.060" end="00:57.800" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:53.060" end="00:53.500">限</span><span begin="00:53.500" end="00:53.730">り</span><span begin="00:53.780" end="00:54.110">の</span><span begin="00:54.200" end="00:54.650">無</span><span begin="00:54.650" end="00:54.870">い</span><span begin="00:54.960" end="00:55.760">時</span><span begin="00:55.850" end="00:56.210">を</span><span begin="00:56.290" end="00:56.720">越</span><span begin="00:56.720" end="00:56.880">え</span><span begin="00:56.950" end="00:57.190">て</span><span begin="00:57.190" end="00:57.800">今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">跨越无尽的光阴 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">跨越無盡的光陰 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crossing over limitless time now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝없는 시간을 넘어 지금</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Traversant un temps infini maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cruzando ahora el tiempo ilimitado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jetzt die grenzenlose Zeit überwindend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cruzando o tempo sem limites agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Преодолев безграничное время сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Superando un tempo infinito ora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kagiri no nai toki o koete ima</span></p>
      <p begin="00:58.100" end="01:01.010" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:58.100" end="00:58.530">そ</span><span begin="00:58.650" end="00:58.910">の</span><span begin="00:59.020" end="00:59.480">手</span><span begin="00:59.550" end="00:59.650">に</span><span begin="00:59.710" end="00:59.990">触</span><span begin="00:59.990" end="01:00.100">れ</span><span begin="01:00.170" end="01:00.430">さ</span><span begin="01:00.430" end="01:00.530">せ</span><span begin="01:00.530" end="01:01.010">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我触碰你的手吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我觸碰你的手吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let me touch those hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 손에 닿게 해줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi toucher tes mains</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame tocar esas manos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich diese Hand berühren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixe-me tocar nessa mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволь мне коснуться этих рук</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lasciami toccare quelle mani</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono te ni furesasete</span></p>
      <p begin="01:01.320" end="01:04.840" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:01.320" end="01:01.850">黒</span><span begin="01:01.850" end="01:01.960">い</span><span begin="01:02.000" end="01:02.290">感</span><span begin="01:02.350" end="01:02.670">情</span><span begin="01:02.740" end="01:02.950">も</span> <span begin="01:03.210" end="01:03.440">君</span><span begin="01:03.440" end="01:03.580">へ</span><span begin="01:03.620" end="01:04.110">繋</span><span begin="01:04.130" end="01:04.200">ぐ</span> <span begin="01:04.250" end="01:04.580">Pas</span><span begin="01:04.580" end="01:04.840">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕是漆黑的情感 也是连结向你的热情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕是漆黑的情感 也是連結向你的熱情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even black emotions are the Passion connecting to you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">黒い感情も 君へ繋ぐ情熱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">검은 감정도 너에게 이어지는 열정</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même ces émotions noires sont une passion qui me lie à toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso los sentimientos negros son una pasión que me conecta a ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch schwarze Gefühle sind eine Passion die mich mit dir verbindet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Até as emoções sombrias são a Passion que me conecta a você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже темные эмоции это страсть связывающая меня с тобой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche i sentimenti oscuri sono una passione che mi lega a te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuroi kanjou mo kimi e tsunagu Passion</span></p>
      <p begin="01:05.050" end="01:09.090" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:05.050" end="01:05.170">だ</span><span begin="01:05.170" end="01:05.310">か</span><span begin="01:05.310" end="01:05.430">ら</span><span begin="01:05.530" end="01:05.700">どう</span><span begin="01:05.740" end="01:05.880">か</span><span begin="01:05.940" end="01:06.200">す</span><span begin="01:06.230" end="01:06.380">べ</span><span begin="01:06.450" end="01:06.660">て</span> <span begin="01:06.910" end="01:07.290">愛</span><span begin="01:07.360" end="01:07.760">し</span><span begin="01:07.800" end="01:07.970">て</span><span begin="01:07.970" end="01:08.180">欲</span><span begin="01:08.470" end="01:09.090">しい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">所以求求你 将这一切全盘接纳吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">所以求求你 將這一切全盤接納吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So please I want you to love everything</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그러니 부디 이 모든 걸 사랑해 줬으면 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors s'il te plaît j'aimerais que tu aimes tout cela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por eso por favor quiero que lo ames todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Deshalb bitte ich dich alles daran zu lieben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por isso por favor quero que ame tudo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Поэтому прошу полюби их все</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perciò ti prego di amare tutto questo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara douka subete aishite hoshii</span></p>
      <p begin="01:07.800" end="01:11.410" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:07.800" end="01:08.280">限</span><span begin="01:08.280" end="01:08.490">り</span><span begin="01:08.490" end="01:08.880">有</span><span begin="01:08.880" end="01:09.130">る</span><span begin="01:09.220" end="01:09.400">こ</span><span begin="01:09.450" end="01:09.740">の</span><span begin="01:09.790" end="01:10.650">命</span><span begin="01:10.730" end="01:10.960">は</span> <span begin="01:11.050" end="01:11.410">そう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这有限的生命 没错</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這有限的生命 沒錯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This limited life is yes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">유한한 이 생명은 그래</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette vie limitée oui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esta vida limitada sí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses begrenzte Leben ja</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esta vida limitada sim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Да эта конечная жизнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questa vita limitata sì</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kagiri aru kono inochi wa sou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:11.750" end="01:15.820" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:11.750" end="01:12.500">再</span><span begin="01:12.570" end="01:12.810">び</span><span begin="01:12.900" end="01:13.080">出</span><span begin="01:13.140" end="01:13.510">会</span><span begin="01:13.510" end="01:13.760">う</span><span begin="01:13.840" end="01:13.980">た</span><span begin="01:14.050" end="01:14.370">め</span><span begin="01:14.400" end="01:14.760">に</span><span begin="01:14.760" end="01:15.240">在</span><span begin="01:15.240" end="01:15.320">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正是为了与你重逢而存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正是為了與你重逢而存在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Existing to meet again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">다시 만나기 위해 존재하는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Existe pour te rencontrer à nouveau</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Existe para que nos volvamos a encontrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Existiert nur um dir wieder zu begegnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Existe para te encontrar novamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Существует лишь для того чтобы встретиться вновь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Esiste per poterti incontrare di nuovo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Futatabi deau tame ni aru</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:15.210" end="01:15.820"><span begin="01:15.210" end="01:15.820">(Ah)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah</span></span></p>
      <p begin="01:16.100" end="01:19.550" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:16.100" end="01:16.240">絶</span><span begin="01:16.360" end="01:16.720">対</span><span begin="01:16.790" end="01:17.120">的</span><span begin="01:17.120" end="01:17.390">愛</span><span begin="01:17.490" end="01:17.770">情</span> <span begin="01:17.960" end="01:18.200">君</span><span begin="01:18.200" end="01:18.400">と</span><span begin="01:18.400" end="01:18.500">い</span><span begin="01:18.500" end="01:18.590">う</span> <span begin="01:18.640" end="01:18.840">Ob</span><span begin="01:18.950" end="01:19.330">ses</span><span begin="01:19.330" end="01:19.550">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝对的爱情 名为你的执念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕對的愛情 名為你的執念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Absolute affection the Obsession called you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">絶対的愛情 君という執着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">절대적 애정 너라는 집착</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une affection absolue cette obsession qu'on appelle toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un amor absoluto la obsesión que eres tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Absolute Liebe diese Obsession namens du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Afeto absoluto a Obsession chamada você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Абсолютная любовь одержимость по имени «ты»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Amore assoluto l'ossessione chiamata te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zettaiteki aijou kimi to iu Obsession</span></p>
      <p begin="01:19.830" end="01:24.000" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:19.830" end="01:20.040">報</span><span begin="01:20.040" end="01:20.240">い</span><span begin="01:20.300" end="01:20.450">の</span><span begin="01:20.510" end="01:20.640">無</span><span begin="01:20.640" end="01:20.730">い</span><span begin="01:20.730" end="01:21.200">想</span><span begin="01:21.200" end="01:21.490">い</span> <span begin="01:21.650" end="01:22.130">君</span><span begin="01:22.130" end="01:22.530">へ</span><span begin="01:22.610" end="01:22.900">と</span><span begin="01:23.000" end="01:23.930">捧</span><span begin="01:23.930" end="01:24.000">ぐ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将这份毫无回报的思念 尽数奉献于你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將這份毫無回報的思念 盡數奉獻於你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Unrewarded feelings I dedicate to you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보답받지 못할 마음을 너에게 바쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces sentiments sans récompense je te les dédie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te dedico estos sentimientos sin recompensa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese unbelohnten Gefühle widme ich dir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dedico a você esses sentimentos sem recompensa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Безответные чувства я посвящаю тебе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dedico a te questi sentimenti non corrisposti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukui no nai omoi kimi e to sasagu</span></p>
      <p begin="01:28.860" end="01:30.360" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:28.860" end="01:29.250">もう</span><span begin="01:29.320" end="01:29.440">行</span><span begin="01:29.440" end="01:29.550">き</span><span begin="01:29.550" end="01:29.670">場</span><span begin="01:29.670" end="01:29.780">の</span><span begin="01:29.780" end="01:29.890">な</span><span begin="01:29.890" end="01:29.980">い</span><span begin="01:29.980" end="01:30.090">思</span><span begin="01:30.090" end="01:30.360">考</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">已然无处安放的思绪</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">已然無處安放的思緒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Thoughts with nowhere left to go</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">더 이상 갈 곳 없는 사고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Des pensées qui n'ont plus nulle part où aller</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pensamientos que ya no tienen adónde ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gedanken die nirgendwohin mehr können</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pensamentos que já não têm para onde ir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Мысли которым больше некуда деться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Pensieri che non hanno più un posto dove andare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mou ikiba no nai shikou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:30.470" end="01:31.820" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:30.470" end="01:30.600">曖</span><span begin="01:30.690" end="01:30.910">昧</span><span begin="01:30.910" end="01:31.020">な</span><span begin="01:31.130" end="01:31.420">絶</span><span begin="01:31.480" end="01:31.820">望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">暧昧不清的绝望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">曖昧不清的絕望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ambiguous despair</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애매한 절망</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un désespoir ambigu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una desesperación ambigua</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Vage Verzweiflung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desespero ambíguo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смутное отчаяние</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una disperazione ambigua</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aimai na zetsubou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:32.520" end="01:35.430" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:32.520" end="01:32.920">Oh</span> <span begin="01:33.000" end="01:33.240">暴</span><span begin="01:33.240" end="01:33.370">れ</span><span begin="01:33.370" end="01:33.500">る</span><span begin="01:33.500" end="01:33.700">感</span><span begin="01:33.790" end="01:34.020">情</span><span begin="01:34.020" end="01:34.050">、</span><span begin="01:34.110" end="01:34.300">焦</span><span begin="01:34.360" end="01:34.610">燥</span><span begin="01:34.610" end="01:34.730">を</span><span begin="01:34.840" end="01:35.010">どう</span><span begin="01:35.060" end="01:35.170">し</span><span begin="01:35.170" end="01:35.430">よう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 这狂暴的情感与焦躁 该如何是好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 這狂暴的情感與焦躁 該如何是好</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Oh what should I do with these raging emotions, this impatience</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ああ 暴れる感情 焦燥をどうしよう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 날뛰는 감정, 초조함을 어떡하지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Oh ces émotions violentes que faire de cette frustration</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oh estas emociones desbocadas, qué hago con esta impaciencia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Oh wütende Gefühle was soll ich mit dieser Ungeduld tun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Oh emoções violentas, o que fazer com essa frustração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ох бушующие эмоции что же делать с этой тревогой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Oh cosa dovrei fare con queste emozioni violente e questa frustrazione</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oh abareru kanjou, shousou o dou shiyou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:36.270" end="01:37.630" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:36.270" end="01:36.580">No</span> <span begin="01:36.670" end="01:36.860">止</span><span begin="01:36.860" end="01:36.940">め</span><span begin="01:36.940" end="01:37.020">ら</span><span begin="01:37.020" end="01:37.160">れ</span><span begin="01:37.160" end="01:37.250">な</span><span begin="01:37.250" end="01:37.390">い</span><span begin="01:37.390" end="01:37.490">過</span><span begin="01:37.490" end="01:37.630">剰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不 这是无法抑制的过载</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">不 這是無法抑制的過載</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">No unstoppable excess</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">いや 止められない過剰</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아니 멈출 수 없는 과잉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Non un excès incontrôlable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No un exceso que no se puede detener</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nein ein unaufhaltsamer Überschuss</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No excesso incontrolável</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нет это неудержимый переизбыток</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">No un eccesso inarrestabile</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">No tomerarenai kajou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:37.820" end="01:39.510" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:37.820" end="01:38.090">混</span><span begin="01:38.090" end="01:38.220">沌</span><span begin="01:38.270" end="01:38.500">そ</span><span begin="01:38.500" end="01:38.690">れ</span><span begin="01:38.740" end="01:38.840">以</span><span begin="01:38.890" end="01:39.510">上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">比混沌还要更加混沌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">比混沌還要更加混沌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Chaos more than that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">혼돈 그 이상</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le chaos et bien plus encore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Más allá del caos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mehr als nur Chaos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Caos e muito mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хаос и даже больше</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Più del caos</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Konton sore ijou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:39.890" end="01:41.430" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:39.890" end="01:40.280">Though</span> <span begin="01:40.380" end="01:40.630">確</span><span begin="01:40.630" end="01:40.730">か</span><span begin="01:40.730" end="01:40.810">な</span><span begin="01:40.810" end="01:41.120">切</span><span begin="01:41.170" end="01:41.430">望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">然而 却是无比真切的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">然而 卻是無比真切的渴望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Though a certain longing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">それでも 確かな切望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 확실한 갈망</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourtant un désir certain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque es un anhelo certero</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dennoch ein tiefes Verlangen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Though desejo ardente e certo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И всё же это несомненная жажда</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sebbene sia un desiderio certo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Though tashika na setsubou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:41.520" end="01:42.910" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="01:41.520" end="01:41.620">た</span><span begin="01:41.620" end="01:41.720">だ</span><span begin="01:41.720" end="01:41.870">じ</span><span begin="01:41.870" end="01:41.980">っ</span><span begin="01:41.980" end="01:42.110">と</span><span begin="01:42.110" end="01:42.370">抱</span><span begin="01:42.370" end="01:42.440">く</span><span begin="01:42.440" end="01:42.530">希</span><span begin="01:42.570" end="01:42.910">望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只是静静怀抱着的希望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只是靜靜懷抱著的希望</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A hope I just quietly embrace</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그저 가만히 품은 희망</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Gardant juste l'espoir en silence</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una esperanza que solo abrazo en silencio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Eine Hoffnung die ich einfach still umarme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A esperança que apenas abraço em silêncio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Надежда которую я просто тихо обнимаю</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Una speranza che nutro in silenzio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tada jitto daku kibou</span></p>
      <p begin="01:43.090" end="01:44.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="01:43.090" end="01:43.480">How</span> <span begin="01:43.550" end="01:43.830">far</span> <span begin="01:43.890" end="01:44.290">from</span> <span begin="01:44.290" end="01:44.480">you</span> <span begin="01:44.540" end="01:44.970">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻我距离你还有多远</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻我距離你還有多遠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">今 君からどれほど遠いのだろう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금 너에게서 얼마나 멀리 떨어져 있는 걸까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">À quelle distance de toi suis-je maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Qué tan lejos de ti estoy ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wie weit bin ich nun von dir entfernt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A que distância estou de você agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Как же далеко я сейчас от тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Quanto sono lontana da te ora</span></p>
      <p begin="01:45.450" end="01:50.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="01:45.450" end="01:45.680">And</span> <span begin="01:45.760" end="01:46.120">grain</span> <span begin="01:46.170" end="01:46.330">by</span> <span begin="01:46.400" end="01:46.770">grain,</span> <span begin="01:46.840" end="01:47.190">the</span> <span begin="01:47.250" end="01:47.520">sand</span> <span begin="01:47.620" end="01:47.960">ga</span><span begin="01:47.960" end="01:48.130">ther</span><span begin="01:48.130" end="01:48.240">s</span> <span begin="01:48.240" end="01:48.670">in</span> <span begin="01:48.670" end="01:49.060">the</span> <span begin="01:49.160" end="01:50.420">win</span><span begin="01:50.420" end="01:50.450">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">砂砾在狂风中 粒粒聚积</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">砂礫在狂風中 粒粒聚積</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一粒また一粒 風の中で砂が集まっていく</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리고 한 알 한 알, 모래가 바람에 모여들어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et grain par grain le sable s'amasse dans le vent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y grano a grano, la arena se acumula en el viento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und Korn für Korn sammelt sich der Sand im Wind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E grão por grão, a areia se acumula no vento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И песчинка за песчинкой песок собирается на ветру</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E granello dopo granello la sabbia si raccoglie nel vento</span></p>
      <p begin="01:50.980" end="01:54.220" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="01:50.980" end="01:51.290">This</span> <span begin="01:51.290" end="01:51.700">fee</span><span begin="01:51.700" end="01:51.880">ling's</span> <span begin="01:51.880" end="01:52.150">so</span> <span begin="01:52.210" end="01:52.580">pure</span> <span begin="01:52.580" end="01:52.710">it</span> <span begin="01:52.790" end="01:53.010">dri</span><span begin="01:53.010" end="01:53.160">ves</span> <span begin="01:53.160" end="01:53.430">me</span> <span begin="01:53.490" end="01:53.670">more</span> <span begin="01:53.740" end="01:54.190">ma</span><span begin="01:54.190" end="01:54.220">d</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这份感情如此纯粹 反而令我愈发疯狂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這份感情如此純粹 反而令我愈發瘋狂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">この想いはあまりに純粋で さらに私を狂わせる</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 감정은 너무나 순수해서 날 더욱 미치게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce sentiment est si pur qu'il me rend encore plus folle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Este sentimiento es tan puro que me vuelve más loca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Gefühl ist so rein dass es mich noch mehr in den Wahnsinn treibt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esse sentimento é tão puro que me deixa mais louca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это чувство настолько чистое что сводит меня с ума еще сильнее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Questo sentimento è così puro che mi fa impazzire ancora di più</span></p>
      <p begin="01:54.680" end="01:57.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="01:54.680" end="01:54.960">And</span> <span begin="01:55.160" end="01:55.400">I'd</span> <span begin="01:55.620" end="01:55.850">do</span> <span begin="01:56.070" end="01:56.300">a</span><span begin="01:56.300" end="01:56.650">ny</span><span begin="01:56.770" end="01:56.900">thing</span> <span begin="01:56.960" end="01:57.180">for</span> <span begin="01:57.180" end="01:57.320">your</span> <span begin="01:57.460" end="01:57.910">lo</span><span begin="01:57.910" end="01:57.970">ve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为了你的爱 我愿倾尽所有</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為了你的愛 我願傾盡所有</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">君の愛のためなら 何だってする</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너의 사랑을 위해서라면 난 뭐든 할 텐데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et je ferais n'importe quoi pour ton amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y haría cualquier cosa por tu amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Und ich würde alles für deine Liebe tun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E eu faria qualquer coisa pelo seu amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И я сделаю всё ради твоей любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E farei qualsiasi cosa per il tuo amore</span></p>
      <p begin="01:58.600" end="02:00.190" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="01:58.600" end="01:58.930">懐</span><span begin="01:59.040" end="01:59.200">か</span><span begin="01:59.300" end="01:59.520">し</span><span begin="01:59.520" end="01:59.590">む</span><span begin="01:59.640" end="01:59.880">だ</span><span begin="02:00.010" end="02:00.190">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅仅是怀念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅僅是懷念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just feeling nostalgic</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그리워할 뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Juste ressentir de la nostalgie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo recordar con nostalgia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sich nur zu sehnen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas sentindo saudades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Просто вспоминать с тоской</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo provando nostalgia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Natsukashimu dake</span></p>
      <p begin="02:00.430" end="02:02.030" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:00.430" end="02:00.970">慈</span><span begin="02:01.080" end="02:01.370">し</span><span begin="02:01.370" end="02:01.420">む</span><span begin="02:01.470" end="02:01.730">だ</span><span begin="02:01.830" end="02:02.030">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅仅是怜爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅僅是憐愛</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just cherishing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애지중지할 뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Juste chérir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo amar tiernamente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur zu hegen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas sentindo carinho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Просто лелеять в сердце</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo provando affetto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsukushimu dake</span></p>
      <p begin="02:02.240" end="02:03.870" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:02.240" end="02:02.520">そ</span><span begin="02:02.520" end="02:02.630">れ</span><span begin="02:02.760" end="02:02.850">だ</span><span begin="02:03.000" end="02:03.200">け</span><span begin="02:03.200" end="02:03.280">じゃ</span><span begin="02:03.320" end="02:03.550">到</span><span begin="02:03.680" end="02:03.870">底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅仅是这样 到底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅僅是這樣 到底</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just that is absolutely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그것만으론 도저히</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec seulement cela c'est absolument</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo con eso no puedo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das allein reicht absolut nicht aus</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Só com isso de forma alguma</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Одного этого мне ни за что</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo con questo non potrò mai</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore dake ja toutei</span></p>
      <p begin="02:04.140" end="02:05.880" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:04.140" end="02:04.270">満</span><span begin="02:04.370" end="02:04.490">た</span><span begin="02:04.560" end="02:04.840">さ</span><span begin="02:04.840" end="02:05.030">れ</span><span begin="02:05.190" end="02:05.560">な</span><span begin="02:05.560" end="02:05.880">い…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无法得到满足</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無法得到滿足</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Unsatisfied...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">채워지지 않아…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Insatisfaisant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estar satisfecha en absoluto…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Um befriedigt zu werden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Serei preenchida...</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не будет достаточно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Essere soddisfatta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mitasarenai…</span></p>
