      <p begin="02:10.600" end="02:15.540" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="02:10.600" end="02:10.840">有</span><span begin="02:10.840" end="02:11.060">り</span><span begin="02:11.060" end="02:11.900">余</span><span begin="02:11.990" end="02:12.490">る</span><span begin="02:12.490" end="02:13.320">愛</span><span begin="02:13.370" end="02:13.670">の</span><span begin="02:13.820" end="02:14.610">迷</span><span begin="02:14.610" end="02:14.690">う</span><span begin="02:14.740" end="02:14.900">ま</span><span begin="02:14.970" end="02:15.540">ま</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">任由过剩的爱意迷失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">任由過剩的愛意迷失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Remaining lost in this overflowing love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">넘쳐나는 사랑에 헤매는 채로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Perdue dans un amour surabondant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mientras este amor desbordante sigue perdido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Während ich mich in dieser überfließenden Liebe verirre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Perdida neste amor que transborda</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Продолжая блуждать в этой избыточной любви</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perdendomi in questo amore traboccante</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ariamaru ai no mayou mama</span></p>
