      <p begin="02:31.840" end="02:33.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="02:31.840" end="02:31.980">名</span><span begin="02:32.070" end="02:32.450">前</span><span begin="02:32.510" end="02:32.670">を</span><span begin="02:32.720" end="02:32.800">呼</span><span begin="02:32.880" end="02:33.160">ん</span><span begin="02:33.210" end="02:33.400">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呼唤我的名字吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">呼喚我的名字吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Call my name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이름을 부르고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Appelle mon nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Llama mi nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ruf meinen Namen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Chame meu nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Назови мое имя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiama il mio nome</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namae o yonde</span></p>
      <p begin="02:33.640" end="02:35.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="02:33.640" end="02:34.070">愛</span><span begin="02:34.130" end="02:34.290">で</span><span begin="02:34.360" end="02:34.720">応</span><span begin="02:34.720" end="02:34.970">え</span><span begin="02:35.070" end="02:35.230">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用爱来回应我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用愛來回應我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Respond with love</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑으로 대답해 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Réponds par l'amour</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Respóndeme con amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Antworte mit Liebe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Responda com amor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ответь мне любовью</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rispondimi con amore</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai de kotaete</span></p>
      <p begin="02:35.460" end="02:37.120" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="02:35.460" end="02:35.750">そ</span><span begin="02:35.750" end="02:35.910">れ</span><span begin="02:35.980" end="02:36.100">だ</span><span begin="02:36.200" end="02:36.400">け</span><span begin="02:36.430" end="02:36.520">の</span><span begin="02:36.560" end="02:37.120">夢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅仅是这样的梦境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅僅是這樣的夢境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just that kind of dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그저 그것뿐인 꿈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rien que ce rêve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo es ese sueño</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nur dieser eine Traum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas esse sonho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лишь такая мечта</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È soltanto questo il mio sogno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sore dake no yume</span></p>
      <p begin="02:38.970" end="02:40.330" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="02:38.970" end="02:39.150">I</span> <span begin="02:39.210" end="02:39.520">just</span> <span begin="02:39.520" end="02:39.660">wan</span><span begin="02:39.720" end="02:39.860">ted</span> <span begin="02:39.940" end="02:40.330">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我想要的只有你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我想要的只有你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ただ君が欲しかった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">난 그저 너를 원했을 뿐이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je te voulais juste toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo te quería a ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich wollte einfach nur dich</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu só queria você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я просто хотела тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Volevo solo te</span></p>
      <p begin="02:40.130" end="02:44.890" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="02:40.130" end="02:40.590">限</span><span begin="02:40.590" end="02:40.750">り</span><span begin="02:40.800" end="02:41.160">の</span><span begin="02:41.260" end="02:41.730">無</span><span begin="02:41.730" end="02:41.950">い</span><span begin="02:42.010" end="02:42.840">時</span><span begin="02:42.900" end="02:43.290">を</span><span begin="02:43.370" end="02:43.820">越</span><span begin="02:43.820" end="02:43.990">え</span><span begin="02:44.050" end="02:44.300">て</span><span begin="02:44.300" end="02:44.890">今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">跨越无尽的光阴 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">跨越無盡的光陰 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Crossing over limitless time now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끝없는 시간을 넘어 지금</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Traversant un temps infini maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Cruzando ahora el tiempo ilimitado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jetzt die grenzenlose Zeit überwindend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cruzando o tempo sem limites agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Преодолев безграничное время сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Superando un tempo infinito ora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kagiri no nai toki o koete ima</span></p>
      <p begin="02:45.170" end="02:48.100" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="02:45.170" end="02:45.600">そ</span><span begin="02:45.680" end="02:45.980">の</span><span begin="02:46.090" end="02:46.490">手</span><span begin="02:46.580" end="02:46.680">に</span><span begin="02:46.760" end="02:47.070">触</span><span begin="02:47.070" end="02:47.180">れ</span><span begin="02:47.250" end="02:47.500">さ</span><span begin="02:47.500" end="02:47.610">せ</span><span begin="02:47.610" end="02:48.100">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我触碰你的手吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我觸碰你的手吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let me touch those hands</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 손에 닿게 해줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Laisse-moi toucher tes mains</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame tocar esas manos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich diese Hand berühren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deixe-me tocar nessa mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Позволь мне коснуться этих рук</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Lasciami toccare quelle mani</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono te ni furesasete</span></p>
      <p begin="02:48.390" end="02:51.860" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L49"><span begin="02:48.390" end="02:48.890">黒</span><span begin="02:48.890" end="02:49.000">い</span><span begin="02:49.060" end="02:49.360">感</span><span begin="02:49.430" end="02:49.710">情</span><span begin="02:49.800" end="02:50.020">も</span> <span begin="02:50.280" end="02:50.520">君</span><span begin="02:50.520" end="02:50.660">へ</span><span begin="02:50.720" end="02:51.170">繋</span><span begin="02:51.170" end="02:51.240">ぐ</span> <span begin="02:51.300" end="02:51.630">Pas</span><span begin="02:51.630" end="02:51.860">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕是漆黑的情感 也是连结向你的热情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕是漆黑的情感 也是連結向你的熱情</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even black emotions are the Passion connecting to you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">黒い感情も 君へ繋ぐ情熱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">검은 감정도 너에게 이어지는 열정</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même ces émotions noires sont une passion qui me lie à toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso los sentimientos negros son una pasión que me conecta a ti</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch schwarze Gefühle sind eine Passion die mich mit dir verbindet</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Até as emoções sombrias são a Passion que me conecta a você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже темные эмоции это страсть связывающая меня с тобой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche i sentimenti oscuri sono una passione che mi lega a te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuroi kanjou mo kimi e tsunagu Passion</span></p>
