      <p begin="03:17.970" end="03:21.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L57"><span begin="03:17.970" end="03:18.170">盲</span><span begin="03:18.230" end="03:18.510">目</span><span begin="03:18.700" end="03:19.040">的</span><span begin="03:19.040" end="03:19.380">願</span><span begin="03:19.380" end="03:19.590">望</span> <span begin="03:19.850" end="03:20.040">永</span><span begin="03:20.040" end="03:20.280">遠</span><span begin="03:20.280" end="03:20.430">の</span> <span begin="03:20.490" end="03:20.720">De</span><span begin="03:20.800" end="03:21.090">vo</span><span begin="03:21.170" end="03:21.400">tion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">盲目的愿望 永恒的奉献</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">盲目的願望 永恆的奉獻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Blind desire eternal Devotion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">盲目的願望 永遠の献身</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">맹목적 소망 영원한 헌신</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un désir aveugle une dévotion éternelle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un deseo ciego una devoción eterna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein blinder Wunsch diese ewige Devotion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desejo cego Devotion eterna</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слепое желание вечная преданность</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Desiderio cieco una devozione eterna</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mouteki ganbou eien no Devotion</span></p>
      <p begin="03:21.640" end="03:25.600" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L58"><span begin="03:21.640" end="03:21.880">こ</span><span begin="03:21.880" end="03:22.050">れ</span><span begin="03:22.130" end="03:22.490">が</span><span begin="03:22.570" end="03:23.000">最</span><span begin="03:23.070" end="03:23.480">期</span><span begin="03:23.540" end="03:23.860">に</span><span begin="03:24.030" end="03:24.360">な</span><span begin="03:24.360" end="03:24.440">っ</span><span begin="03:24.440" end="03:24.750">た</span><span begin="03:24.750" end="03:24.930">っ</span><span begin="03:24.930" end="03:25.140">て</span><span begin="03:25.140" end="03:25.600">いい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即便这就是最后一次也无妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即便這就是最後一次也無妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">It's fine even if this becomes the end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이것이 마지막이 된다 해도 좋아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas grave si c'est la fin</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No me importa si este es el final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es ist mir egal ob dies das Ende ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tudo bem se este for o fim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть даже это станет моим концом</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non mi importa se questa dovesse essere la fine</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kore ga saigo ni nattatte ii</span></p>
      <p begin="03:24.670" end="03:30.600" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L59"><span begin="03:24.670" end="03:25.080">The</span> <span begin="03:25.150" end="03:25.500">en</span><span begin="03:25.500" end="03:25.550">d</span> <span begin="03:25.550" end="03:25.730">i</span><span begin="03:25.730" end="03:25.820">s</span> <span begin="03:25.820" end="03:26.010">here</span> <span begin="03:26.070" end="03:26.590">now,</span> <span begin="03:26.980" end="03:27.220">but</span> <span begin="03:27.350" end="03:27.670">my</span> <span begin="03:27.670" end="03:27.830">love</span> <span begin="03:27.830" end="03:28.250">still</span> <span begin="03:28.320" end="03:30.480">li</span><span begin="03:30.480" end="03:30.600">ves</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">终局已然降临 但我的爱永存</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">終局已然降臨 但我的愛永存</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">終わりは今ここにある それでも私の愛はまだ生きている</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금 끝이 다가왔지만, 내 사랑은 여전히 살아있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La fin est là maintenant mais mon amour vit toujours</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El final está aquí ahora, pero mi amor aún vive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Ende ist nun hier doch meine Liebe lebt weiter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fim está aqui agora, mas meu amor ainda vive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Конец уже здесь но моя любовь продолжает жить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La fine è qui ora ma il mio amore vive ancora</span></p>
      <p begin="03:29.030" end="03:32.440" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L60"><span begin="03:29.030" end="03:29.420">愛</span><span begin="03:29.500" end="03:29.630">で</span><span begin="03:29.740" end="03:30.140">応</span><span begin="03:30.140" end="03:30.310">え</span><span begin="03:30.450" end="03:30.630">て</span> <span begin="03:30.910" end="03:31.150">そ</span><span begin="03:31.150" end="03:31.290">れ</span><span begin="03:31.400" end="03:31.510">だ</span><span begin="03:31.590" end="03:31.750">け</span><span begin="03:31.800" end="03:31.940">の</span><span begin="03:31.940" end="03:32.440">夢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用爱来回应我吧 仅仅是这样的梦境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用愛來回應我吧 僅僅是這樣的夢境</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Respond with love just that kind of dream</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사랑으로 대답해 줘 그저 그것뿐인 꿈</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Réponds par l'amour rien que ce rêve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Respóndeme con amor solo es ese sueño</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Antworte mit Liebe nur dieser eine Traum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Responda com amor apenas esse sonho</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ответь мне любовью лишь такая мечта</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rispondimi con amore è soltanto questo il mio sogno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai de kotaete sore dake no yume</span></p>
      <p begin="03:32.710" end="03:36.170" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L61"><span begin="03:32.710" end="03:32.880">絶</span><span begin="03:32.930" end="03:33.250">対</span><span begin="03:33.380" end="03:33.700">的</span><span begin="03:33.700" end="03:34.020">愛</span><span begin="03:34.080" end="03:34.330">情</span> <span begin="03:34.560" end="03:34.760">君</span><span begin="03:34.800" end="03:35.020">と</span><span begin="03:35.020" end="03:35.130">い</span><span begin="03:35.130" end="03:35.260">う</span> <span begin="03:35.260" end="03:35.470">Ob</span><span begin="03:35.540" end="03:35.930">ses</span><span begin="03:35.930" end="03:36.170">sion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝对的爱情 名为你的执念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕對的愛情 名為你的執念</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Absolute affection the Obsession called you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">絶対的愛情 君という執着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">절대적 애정 너라는 집착</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Une affection absolue cette obsession qu'on appelle toi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un amor absoluto la obsesión que eres tú</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Absolute Liebe diese Obsession namens du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Afeto absoluto a Obsession chamada você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Абсолютная любовь одержимость по имени «ты»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Amore assoluto l'ossessione chiamata te</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zettaiteki aijou kimi to iu Obsession</span></p>
      <p begin="03:36.420" end="03:40.660" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L62"><span begin="03:36.420" end="03:36.660">報</span><span begin="03:36.660" end="03:36.850">い</span><span begin="03:36.910" end="03:37.010">の</span><span begin="03:37.110" end="03:37.260">無</span><span begin="03:37.260" end="03:37.340">い</span><span begin="03:37.340" end="03:37.820">想</span><span begin="03:37.820" end="03:38.030">い</span> <span begin="03:38.250" end="03:38.740">君</span><span begin="03:38.740" end="03:39.100">へ</span><span begin="03:39.210" end="03:39.480">と</span><span begin="03:39.590" end="03:40.510">捧</span><span begin="03:40.510" end="03:40.660">ぐ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将这份毫无回报的思念 尽数奉献于你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將這份毫無回報的思念 盡數奉獻於你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Unrewarded feelings I dedicate to you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보답받지 못할 마음을 너에게 바쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ces sentiments sans récompense je te les dédie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Te dedico estos sentimientos sin recompensa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diese unbelohnten Gefühle widme ich dir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dedico a você esses sentimentos sem recompensa</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Безответные чувства я посвящаю тебе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dedico a te questi sentimenti non corrisposti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mukui no nai omoi kimi e to sasagu</span></p>
